 This package provides scripts to work with tarantool configuration
 and log files.

Package: tarantool
Architecture: i386 amd64 armhf arm64
Priority: optional
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, netbase, binutils, libgomp1,
